killing 16 Afghan civilians on March 11 will likely be to flown
to the U.S. from  Kuwait  and held at the maximum security
military prison at Fort Leavenworth, Kansas, a defense official
said today.  The official, who spoke on the condition of anonymity
because the case is still being investigated, said it still
